# CHIMERA Postfix Header Checks
# Basic header filtering for improved deliverability

# Remove sensitive headers that might cause issues
/^Received:/ IGNORE

# Check for proper Message-ID format
/^Message-ID:.*$/ OK

# Basic spam checks (reject obvious spam patterns)
/^Subject:.*\b(?:viagra|casino|lottery|winner)\b/ REJECT Spam content detected
/^Subject:.*\b(?:urgent|emergency|crisis)\b.*\b(?:action|respond|reply)\b/ WARN Potential urgency spam

# Allow legitimate headers
/^X-.*:.*$/ OK
/^List-.*:.*$/ OK

# Reject malformed From headers
/^From:.*<.*>.*$/ OK
/^From:.*[^<]*$/ REJECT Malformed From header

# Allow DKIM signatures
/^DKIM-Signature:/ OK

